        <h2>TIP 2: Int Your Teammates </h2>
        <img src = "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/N08sUOWBaVk/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="inting sion">
        
        <h2>Unlike Yasuo, who does not hit his powerspike until 0/10, Sion gets stronger the more times he dies. Because sion respawns after every death, you can run it down mid and take all of your opponents towers. Doesn't matter if you int ur teammates so long as you win.</h2>
